title: Episode 318: Beefin' in Real Time (Feat. Jhonni Blaze)
itunes:title: Episode 318: Beefin' in Real Time (Feat. Jhonni Blaze)
description:
Musician, Jhonni Blaze joins the ladies of Lip Service to promote her latest singles, "I'm Emotions" & "Toxic!" Jhonni opens up and gets vulnerable when discussing her abusive relationships, both physically and emotionally. Jhonni is also currently having issues with her ex...that's not her ex....but it's her ex, and Angela helps text him, to try and work through the fight! Enjoy!
